{"tid":2009887,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港警察聯同富臨酒樓，打壓員工","createTime":"2020-05-10T05:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T02:09:04.000Z","uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"645a34c582e09a76377a60023cd81965df1a4c02","tid":2009887,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"富臨集團假借放無薪假，逃避支付員工遣散費。今日是母親節，民協和職工盟屬會飲食及酒店業職工總會早上再到位於美孚的富臨皇宮抗議。經理隨即報警，在酒樓內的便衣警察隨即殺出，和到場的軍裝警員「裡應外合」，驅趕參與行動的民協及工會成員，並拘捕職工盟組織幹事林小薇等共2人。<br />\n<br />\n警察到場後立刻配合富臨行動，該名<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>經理高呼「好嘢，警察嚟拉哂班仆街。」</strong></span>該批軍裝警員先將在場的記者趕到樓梯下，並開咪指參與行動的人士已觸犯「禁聚令」。多名軍裝警員包圍參與行動人士，何啟明、吳敏兒、楊彧和其助理許垣垣多次和警察及酒樓員工發生衝突，吳敏兒一度激落淚，「富臨你係咪人嚟？」<br />\n<br />\n詳情 ：<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073236&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpX88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=f7179fb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073236&h=f0f8b7bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073236</a>"},{"pid":"3b5859343dedca9ee83682e872e31fb6a9d777f0","tid":2009887,"uid":321854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵死啦"},{"pid":"8a22db1fcba23cfdc86e2422e43871b2ee0d3f7d","tid":2009887,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:09:04.000Z","msg":"美心好啲，炒咗先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}